Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
5 brand new high quality strata units well situated at Monaro Business Park in Hume. Monaro Business Park is approximately 10 kilometres south east of the Canberra CBD and provides easy access to major arterial roads.

The development comprises tilt slab construction with high clearance, mezzanine office space, allocated car parks and high roller door access. The development has been cleverly designed for semi trailer access (providing a turning circle) and air conditioned mezzanine with energy efficient double glazed windows. The lighting is censored to save on electricity. High bay lighting has been included in each unit along with a clear roof sheet to allow extra natural light. Amenities include disabled toilets, shower and kitchens. These units are suitable for many types of businesses.

Unit 1     462sqm warehouse + 58sqm mezzanine = 520sqm     SOLD
Unit 2     462sqm warehouse + 55sqm mezzanine = 517sqm     $909,400
Unit 3     462sqm warehouse + 56sqm mezzanine = 518sqm     $887,600
Unit 4     464sqm warehouse + 56sqm mezzanine = 520sqm     LEASED
Unit 5     435sqm warehouse + 62sqm mezzanine = 497sqm     SOLD

Office space of approx.188m2 on 2 levels, a number of seperate offices, meeting room, kitchen, bathroom amenities, reception area, ducted gas heating and evaporative cooling. The 188m2 warehouse is clearspan and high clearance, accessed via a door from the office.  Total floor area - 376sqm.  Annual Rent - $48,880 +GST

The warehouse can be joined with the addacent warehouse (measuring 304m2) to create a total floor area of 680sqm (188sqm office with 492m2 warehouse).  Total floor area - 680sqm.  Annual Rent - $88,400 +GST

The site has security gates, car parking and signage opportunites.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Office & warehouse for lease in Hume

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
82 Sheppard Street is a clean and tidy freestanding warehouse/office facility measuring a total of 1,980sqm with a secure yard area on a single title block measuring 4,224sqm.

The property comprises:

- 1,584sqm clear span warehouse with 8 roller doors, clearance heights from 3.9m - 5.9m, fully sprinkled and heated;

- 84sqm secure cage with T4 security clearance;

- 312sqm air conditioned office with open plan reception area, 4 separate offices, a large boardroom, operations room, male/female/disabled toilets, shower and lunch room / kitchen.

The property would ideally suit storage and/or logistics.

Call CBRE to discuss your requirements.
